/*
  NWC Review Kit — VANILLA build.

  A dependency-free, no-build drop-in of the review kit (slate + review nav +
  in-page commenting) for plain HTML/CSS/JS sites, including HubSpot-ready
  static builds. It is a straight port of the React kit (see ../src); the UI is
  built imperatively and the pure logic (Supabase REST, element anchoring, rich
  context capture) is the same.

  USAGE on any static site — include on every page:
    <script>
      window.NWC_REVIEW_CONFIG = { projectId, supabaseUrl, supabaseAnonKey,
        brand:{name,logo,accent}, bar:{position,autoHide}, slate:{...}, pages:[...] };
    </script>
    <script src="/nwc-review-kit.js" defer></script>
  Mark the review landing page's slate mount point with:  <div data-nwc-slate></div>
  Remove both <script> lines (and the slate div) before porting to HubSpot.

  Config shape mirrors src/config.ts (ReviewConfig). It is review-only: strip it
  for production.
*/
